        <p>As I begin my journey as a frontend developer, I am filled with excitement and a bit of trepidation. The thrill of turning design concepts into fully functional websites is invigorating, though I often face challenges with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Each debugging session teaches me more about browser compatibility and problem-solving, enhancing my technical skills and confidence. Every project I complete is a step forward in my growth, blending creativity with practical experience.</p>

        <h3>What I expect</h3>
